<bookmark xml-lang="en-US" branch="hid/.uno:ZoomIn" id="bm_id3153190" localize="false"/>
<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3153770" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="1"><link href="text/smath/01/03040000.xhp" name="Zoom In">Zoom In</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154490" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".">Increases the display scale of the formula by 25%.</ahelp> The current zoom factor is displayed on the status bar. A selection of available zoom options is accessible through the <link href="text/shared/00/00000001.xhp#kontextmenue" name="context menu">context menu</link>. The context menu in the work area also contains zoom commands.</paragraph>
